      "text": [
        ": «مَرِضَ أَبِي عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَوْمَ اَلْأَضْحَى فَصَلَّى فِي بَيْتِهِ رَكْعَتَيْنِ ثُمَّ ضَحَّى."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1458 - Mansur ibn Hazim narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) who said:\n\"My father (as) fell ill on the day of Eid al-Adha, so he prayed two units (rak'ahs) in his home and then offered the sacrifice.\""
